e-mail: promed@usa.healthnet.org
[I was at a meeting this Thursday with a very senior ARS veterinarian with
laboratory experience who spoke very enthusiastically of this appointment.
Ames has been somewhat adrift for some time and needs someone with vision
and ability. USDA is to be congratulated for looking outside its own ranks
and the US universities to fill this important position. - Mod.MHJ]
